{"tid":1588530,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"近期活動有點失焦 請全力煲大Chinazi 副線警暴","createTime":"2019-09-23T00:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T11:08:09.000Z","uid":15828,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f730bac929b1d9c6bf0a0777e700b8028afc87d5","tid":1588530,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:52:48.000Z","msg":"政府最近有意圖將焦點轉移去警暴，依家活動係比較散亂矇糊，每次就係好嬲班狗，然後要屌鳩佢地，再俾人拉，人地嘅觀感係我地打住五大訴求嘅旗號去破壞。<br />\n<br />\n從前我地每做一件事都有宣言去解釋，依家每個活動都冇宣言冇文宣去解釋，跟得唔貼嘅就會lost，解釋唔到比淺黃中間聽，做唔到政治傳播。<br />\n<br />\n我建議係大家有新行動要講明原因，點解搞SHK，點解搞美心，點解搞港鐵。<br />\n<br />\n另外都要定期出宣言同加強記招講明五大訴求仲未收貨，我地要重新set deadline。<br />\n<br />\n10&middot;1國慶黎到，依家要全城狂煲chinazi（國際戰線）gphone同hocc已經用共產恐怖主義去說服其他國家支持我地，我地都要做D嘢去爭取曝光同新聞air time，義士重要警暴重要，但只可以做副線，主線永遠係反共同五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"adac7f59b3f33b6ddf86777defe8960a555842fd","tid":1588530,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:54:20.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e57298582fb8be7e98e66aa13a270751b4a71885","tid":1588530,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:54:31.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"5ebb5fb3c09b52ecf673e64948e4639e4f39d7e2","tid":1588530,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:54:43.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"3a39837cb103d1f58ed0d18de878f8b15a81c92c","tid":1588530,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"e2aad491b8a31ed53a8fe12d3a4c18316f4235ea","tid":1588530,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:55:08.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"cac220f34fbbed5ac07908149ffdf7301acb5e9b","tid":1588530,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:55:20.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"091938e9a98ebd6e9a0dfc580a356434a90db027","tid":1588530,"uid":15828,